<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1921-09-06T15:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1921-09-06T15:00:00-05:00" n="649" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d649">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">860c.516/113: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Poland</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Gibson</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-09-06T16:00:00-04:00"><hi rend="italic">September 6,
                                        1921—4 p.m.</hi></date></dateline></opener>
                        <p>186. Your 199, August 31, 7 p.m.</p>
                        <p>In your discretion, make representations as you suggest.</p>
                        <p>Your 892 not yet received.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
